          <h3>Wide Gravel Driveways — Easy Loading &amp; Unloading</h3>
          <p>Our <strong>wide, well-maintained gravel driveways</strong> give you room to back in a full-size truck or trailer with ease. <strong>High-security steel doors and locks</strong> on every container — your belongings stay protected and private.</p>
          <div class="caption-highlights">
            <span class="caption-tag">Wide Driveways</span>
            <span class="caption-tag">Truck &amp; Trailer Access</span>
            <span class="caption-tag">Steel Doors &amp; Locks</span>
