      </div>

      <!-- Photo 3 -->
      <div class="photo-feature">
        <img
          src="pictures/Row40Foot1.webp"
          alt="Rows of 40ft storage containers for rent at Fort Knox Self Storage — Vernal Utah Uintah Basin"
          loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675">
        <div class="photo-feature-caption">
          <h3>Rows of Containers Ready to Rent</h3>
          <p>Multiple 40ft containers available for <strong>rent or purchase</strong> right here in the Uintah Basin. Each unit is inspected and maintained to keep your belongings safe, dry, and pest-free.</p>
          <p>Call <strong>James Richards</strong> directly: <a href="tel:4358287710" style="color: var(--primary-dark); font-weight: bold;">435-828-7710</a> — same-day move-in usually available.</p>
          <div class="caption-highlights">
            <span class="caption-tag">Rent or Buy</span>
            <span class="caption-tag">Vernal, UT</span>
            <span class="caption-tag">Same-Day Move-In</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


